data.description: Introducing your new private estate! Surrounded by peace and plenty of land, you will enjoy this craftsman beauty of about 3000sqt. Choose anywhere to sit on the wrap around porch/deck that covers 3/4 of the home. Hardwood floors throughout the home, with bonus room on first floor. Enjoy the pool and family events in the backyard or take the go-karts and toys for a drive through out the property. RV Pad parking with electricity and hooks located on the property. Home Warranty included with purchased. Preferred closing attorney is Brittany Jones @ The Hawes Law Firm.
